# StudentMaster AI вЂ” Backend

> Complete Node.js + Express + MongoDB backend with 7 AI-powered student features.

**Architecture**
- **Backend**: Express.js on Node.js (port **8000**)
- **Database**: MongoDB with 7 Mongoose schemas
- **Features**: Presentation Coach, English Guru, YouTube Quality, Career Predictor, Daily Manager, Brain Dashboard, India-First Localization
- **Deployment**: Docker + docker-compose ready

## рџЏѓвЂЌв™‚пёЏ Quick Start

### Backend (Node.js + Express)
```bash
cd backend && npm install && npm run dev
```

### Frontend (React + Three.js)
```bash
cd frontend && npm install && npm run dev
```

The frontвЂ‘end uses **Vite** and runs on **http://localhost:3000**. It currently displays a placeholder page вЂ” extend it with components for each feature.

### Environment Setup
Add MongoDB Atlas connection to `.env`:
```
MONGO_URI=mongodb+srv://admin:PASSWORD@cluster0.xxx.mongodb.net/studentmaster
```

**Runs on:**
- Backend: http://localhost:8000
- Frontend: http://localhost:5173

### Docker Setup

```bash
docker-compose up --build
```

Starts:
- Node.js backend (port 8000)
- MongoDB (port 27017)

## рџ“љ API Routes вЂ” 7 Features

All endpoints follow REST conventions and return JSON.

### 1пёЏвѓЈ Presentation Coach
- **POST** `/api/presentation/analyze` вЂ” Analyze speech transcript
  - body: `{ transcript: string, duration_seconds?: number }`
  - returns: `{ score, voice_confidence, eye_contact, filler_count, pacing_wpm, tips }`

### 2пёЏвѓЈ English Speaking Guru
- **POST** `/api/english/analyze` вЂ” Fluency & grammar analysis
  - body: `{ text: string, interview_question?: string }`
  - returns: `{ fluency_score, readability_score, fluency_wpm, corrections, exercises, lexical_diversity }`

### 3пёЏвѓЈ YouTube Quality Checker
- **POST** `/api/youtube/analyze` вЂ” Video metadata scoring
  - body: `{ title, description, tags[], transcript?, view_count?, like_count? }`
  - returns: `{ score, relevance_score, sentiment_score, tips, breakdown }`

### 4пёЏвѓЈ Career Predictor 2030
- **POST** `/api/career/predict` вЂ” Career path prediction
  - body: `{ skills?: [], interests?: [], gpa?: number, top?: number }`
  - returns: `{ results: [...{ career_id, job_match, salary_prediction, missing_skills, resources }] }`

### 5пёЏвѓЈ Daily Life Manager
- **POST** `/api/daily/tasks` вЂ” Create task
- **GET** `/api/daily/tasks` вЂ” List tasks
- **GET** `/api/daily/tasks/:id` вЂ” Get task
- **PUT** `/api/daily/tasks/:id` вЂ” Update task
- **DELETE** `/api/daily/tasks/:id` вЂ” Delete task
- **POST** `/api/daily/plan` вЂ” Generate daily schedule

### 6пёЏвѓЈ 3D Brain Dashboard
- **GET** `/api/brain/metrics?user_id=...` вЂ” Get brain region scores
  - returns: `{ brain_score, region_scores: { prefrontal_cortex, hippocampus, ... }, orb_scores: { presentation, english, youtube, ... } }`

### 7пёЏвѓЈ India-First Localization
- **GET** `/api/india/localize?lang=hi|en` вЂ” Localized recommendations
  - returns: `{ locale, recommendations: { topSectors, scholarships, govtPrograms, hiringTips } }`

