## рџ“Љ Database Collections

| Collection | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `users` | Student profiles with college, language, GPA |
| `presentations` | Presentation analysis results |
| `english_sessions` | English fluency records |
| `youtube_analysis` | Video quality analysis |
| `career_profiles` | Career path predictions |
| `tasks` | Daily task management |
| `dashboard_data` | Aggregated metrics for UI |

