## рџЋЇ Sample Requests

### Presentation Analysis
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/api/presentation/analyze \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "transcript": "Um hello everyone today I want to talk about machine learning basically it is really important",
    "duration_seconds": 30
  }'
```

### English Fluency Check
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/api/english/analyze \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "text": "I was given the project and it was completed by the team. We need more testing."
  }'
```

### Career Prediction
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/api/career/predict \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "skills": ["Python", "SQL", "Machine Learning"],
    "gpa": 3.7,
    "top": 3
  }'
```

### Get Brain Metrics
```bash
curl http://localhost:8000/api/brain/metrics
```

### Localized Content
```bash
curl 'http://localhost:8000/api/india/localize?lang=hi'
```

